#include <gfs-input-files-list.h>

Detailed Description

Input file node data structure.

This data structure is used for the input files linked list as a node.

input_fileT::ptr

Input file pointer.

This is a pointer to an input file. The program uses this pointer in order to open and read the contents of an input file.

This is a pointer to a file path. The program uses this file path in order to open an input file. Also, in some places it is printed.
